# Keep the ClusterFuzzLite build context (RFC 0015 Phase 2) small: the
# `.clusterfuzzlite/Dockerfile` does `COPY . $SRC/ourios`, so exclude VCS
# data, build outputs, and the fuzz working dirs (the committed sources,
# fuzz/fuzz_targets, fuzz/seeds, and the manifests are all kept).
.git/
target/
fuzz/target/
fuzz/corpus/
fuzz/artifacts/
fuzz/coverage/
book/
scratch/
